title: 92: Lisa's Hungry Girl Success Story
itunes:title: Lisa's Hungry Girl Success Story
description: In today’s episode, Jamie goes one on one with Lisa about her road to weight-loss success and how she built the Hungry Girl brand! Lisa shares how she lost the weight, how she maintains it, how and why she came up with Hungry Girl, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, Lisa’s three pieces of advice for anyone struggling to achieve their weight-loss goals. This is a can’t-miss episode for all HG fans! When you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for some behind-the-scenes HG fun!
itunes:summary: Have you ever wondered how Lisa became Hungry Girl? Then this is the episode for you!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
